; CHECK_COLLISION -- test the player against the tower/hazards and apply the
; result.
;
; Used by the routine at #R$8240.
;
; .
;
; Dispatches on player_state ($60C0):
; .
; 7 = invulnerable/idle -> no test (RET)
; .
; 4 = check a height window ($60BF in $0A..$1E)
; .
; 8 = RET else test flag $60C5.
; .
; Calls $895B (carry = hit).
; .
; On a hit it patches the value at $8A49 (SELF-MODIFYING: $14/$0F/$20 select
; the bump/death response used downstream) and branches into the hit handler.
; .
; i8080 PORT: the LD ($8A49),A se
