; EXPAND_SPRITE_A -- unrolled copy of a sprite/mask definition from (HL) to
; (DE), terminated by $FF.
;
; Used by the routine at #R$8CC2.
;
; .
;
; The alternating OR $00 / AND $00 immediates are SELF-MODIFIED (by
; calc_sprite_shift) to apply the per-column shift mask.
; .
; Clobbers: A,DE,HL.
; .
; i8080: self-modifying immediates -- a port may instead pass the mask in a
; register and AND/OR it.
