; ADD_BCD_SCORE -- add HL (16-bit BCD delta) to the active player's 4-byte BCD
; score (lives_p1 selects $6043 or $6047), with DAA carry propagation across
; all 4 bytes.
;
; Used by the routine at #R$A727.
;
; .
;
; In: HL=BCD delta, lives_p1=index.
; .
; Clobbers: A,B,C,DE.
; .
; i8080: DAA exists but only valid after ADD/ADC (as used here).
